biography: Tim Bossenmaier works as a Data Engineer at inovex. There he develops and builds modern data infrastructures in customer projects, from streaming ETL pipelines to data catalogs. He is also a developer and member of the project management committee of Apache StreamPipes, an open source solution for IoT data analysis.
